title: Today's Dream
content: Last night I had a dream that I was riding a flying beagle through the andromeda galaxy. It was just ok, but then We went to I hop, and the waiter was like, 'NO DOGS ALOWED'! and we had to leave.

title: Meditation
content: At the end of the day it is nice to reflect on the ups and downs of life. letting the mind rise and flow in vibration like the tide is pulled by the moon. Then all is one, and one is nothing...

title: Aliens next door
content: I swear the Jacobsons next door are not from this planet. We're going to hang out tomorrow. Looking forward to it.

title: We're going on a trip!
content: So... Totally went to space today with the Jacobsons. We were flying through the Andromeda Galaxy when suddenly we stopped to eat at some alien restauraunt. They were so rude, and wouldn't let me come in to eat.
